      little markup to use effectively.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card-tabs cyan darken-3">
  <ul class="tabs tabs-fixed-width tabs-transparent">
  <li class="tab"><a href="#test1" class="waves-effect active">Sign In</a></li>
  <li class="tab"><a href="#test2" class="waves-effect">Sign Up</a></li>
  </ul>
  </div>

